CLI Project

Daily_Fitness

What will it show?

3 options : Based On BodyBuilding.com

	1. The Workout Article Of the Day

	2. The Nutrition Article Of the Day

	3. The Supplement article of the Day.

	4. The Motivation Article Of the Day

Introductory Message -

	“Hello! Are you ready to supplement your fitness lifestyle?

		Choose between three options. Press “1” to get the Best Promotional
    Products of the day, press “2” to get the Workout Article of the day and
    press “3” for the Nutritional Article of the day.

	Please proceed with one of  the options above if you are serious about your gains!”

	Article details
   - Title
   - Description
   - URL

Tips From Avi -

1. Plan your gem, imagine your interface
2. Start with the project structure - google
3. Start with the entry point - the file run
4. Force that to build the CLI Interface
5. Stub out the interface
6. Start making things real
7. Discover objects
8. Program
